It’s Sunday, which means The Parenting Show is on TONIGHT! Tune into @am640 Toronto at 9pm EST to join me along with my special guest co-host, comedian and dad @frankspadone and our special guests, comedian and dad @rob_ianni_comedy, and comedian and dad-to-be @notmarcanthony for another awesome “DADS” edition of The Parenting Show! ⁣⁣⁣
⁣
It’s all about Dads tonight and getting @notmarcanthony ready for fatherhood! So join us as we share stories, tips and advice to help him prepare for what’s to come!⁣
⁣
We won’t be short on laughs tonight, so join us because you won’t want to miss it!⁣⁣⁣
⁣
Tune in live, or if you’re not in the Toronto area, be sure to listen live at www.640Toronto.com🎙. ⁣⁣⁣
